[SHORT DESC]
20% chance to flinch the target.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 20% chance to flinch the target. Hits Pokemon using Bounce, Fly, and Sky Drop for double the usual Base Power.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Twister is far too weak to use competitively, and is outclassed by stronger Dragon-type moves, such as Draco Meteor and Dragon Pulse.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/draco_meteor">Draco Meteor</a> has much higher Base Power, but lowers the user's Special Attack by two stages.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/dragon_pulse">Dragon Pulse</a> has no secondary effects but higher Base Power.</p>